aboutText: I'm Aarnav Sanghvi, a Developer with experience in ReactJS, TailwindCSS, and AI. I am a fun, relaxed person who loves being outdoors and exploring the wilderness. My hobbies include hiking, snow shoeing, and skiing, which have all helped me build a strong work ethic, problem-solving skills, and attention to detail. I use the same skills in my development work, and strive to stay up-to-date on the latest technologies and trends. My experience in ReactJS, TailwindCSS, and AI have enabled me to become a well-rounded developer and to deliver the highest quality of work.
